{
  "book": 19,
  "chapter": 102,
  "sections": [
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "heading": "遭難中的祈禱"
    },
    {
      "type": "desc",
      "contents": []
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 1,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "Lord, hear my prayer! Listen to my plea! "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 1,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "Lord, hear my prayer! Listen to my plea!"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 1,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 2,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "Don’t turn away from me in my time of distress. Bend down to listen, and answer me quickly when I call to you. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 2,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "Don’t turn away from me in my time of distress. Bend down to listen, and answer me quickly when I call to you."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 2,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "Don’t turn away from me in my time of distress. Bend down to listen, and answer me quickly when I call to you."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 2,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 3,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "For my days disappear like smoke, and my bones burn like red-hot coals. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 3,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "For my days disappear like smoke, and my bones burn like red-hot coals."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 3,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 4,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "My heart is sick, withered like grass, and I have lost my appetite. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 4,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "My heart is sick, withered like grass, and I have lost my appetite."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 4,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 5,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "Because of my groaning, I am reduced to skin and bones. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 5,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "Because of my groaning, I am reduced to skin and bones."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 5,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 6,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "I am like an owl in the desert, like a little owl in a far-off wilderness. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 6,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "I am like an owl in the desert, like a little owl in a far-off wilderness."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 6,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 7,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "I lie awake, lonely as a solitary bird on the roof. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 7,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "I lie awake, lonely as a solitary bird on the roof."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 7,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 8,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "My enemies taunt me day after day. They mock and curse me. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 8,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "My enemies taunt me day after day. They mock and curse me."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 8,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 9,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "I eat ashes for food. My tears run down into my drink "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 9,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "I eat ashes for food. My tears run down into my drink"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 9,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 10,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "because of your anger and wrath. For you have picked me up and thrown me out. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 10,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "because of your anger and wrath. For you have picked me up and thrown me out."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 10,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 11,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "My life passes as swiftly as the evening shadows. I am withering away like grass. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 11,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "My life passes as swiftly as the evening shadows. I am withering away like grass."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 11,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 12,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "But you, O Lord, will sit on your throne forever. Your fame will endure to every generation. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 12,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "But you, O Lord, will sit on your throne forever. Your fame will endure to every generation."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 12,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 13,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "You will arise and have mercy on Jerusalem— and now is the time to pity her, now is the time you promised to help. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 13,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "You will arise and have mercy on Jerusalem— and now is the time to pity her, now is the time you promised to help."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 13,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "You will arise and have mercy on Jerusalem— and now is the time to pity her, now is the time you promised to help."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 13,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 14,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "For your people love every stone in her walls and cherish even the dust in her streets. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 14,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "For your people love every stone in her walls and cherish even the dust in her streets."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 14,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 15,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "Then the nations will tremble before the Lord. The kings of the earth will tremble before his glory. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 15,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "Then the nations will tremble before the Lord. The kings of the earth will tremble before his glory."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 15,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 16,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "For the Lord will rebuild Jerusalem. He will appear in his glory. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 16,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "For the Lord will rebuild Jerusalem. He will appear in his glory."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 16,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 17,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "He will listen to the prayers of the destitute. He will not reject their pleas. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 17,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "He will listen to the prayers of the destitute. He will not reject their pleas."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 17,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 18,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "Let this be recorded for future generations, so that a people not yet born will praise the Lord. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 18,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "Let this be recorded for future generations, so that a people not yet born will praise the Lord."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 18,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 19,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "Tell them the Lord looked down from his heavenly sanctuary. He looked down to earth from heaven "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 19,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "Tell them the Lord looked down from his heavenly sanctuary. He looked down to earth from heaven"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 19,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 20,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "to hear the groans of the prisoners, to release those condemned to die. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 20,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "to hear the groans of the prisoners, to release those condemned to die."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 20,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 21,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "And so the Lord’s fame will be celebrated in Zion, his praises in Jerusalem, "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 21,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "And so the Lord’s fame will be celebrated in Zion, his praises in Jerusalem,"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 21,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 22,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "when multitudes gather together and kingdoms come to worship the Lord. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 22,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "when multitudes gather together and kingdoms come to worship the Lord."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 22,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 23,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "He broke my strength in midlife, cutting short my days. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 23,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "He broke my strength in midlife, cutting short my days."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 23,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 24,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "But I cried to him, “O my God, who lives forever, don’t take my life while I am so young! "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 24,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "But I cried to him, “O my God, who lives forever, don’t take my life while I am so young!"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 24,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "But I cried to him, “O my God, who lives forever, don’t take my life while I am so young!"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 24,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 25,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "Long ago you laid the foundation of the earth and made the heavens with your hands. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 25,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "Long ago you laid the foundation of the earth and made the heavens with your hands."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 25,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 26,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "They will perish, but you remain forever; they will wear out like old clothing. You will change them like a garment and discard them. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 26,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "They will perish, but you remain forever; they will wear out like old clothing. You will change them like a garment and discard them."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 26,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "They will perish, but you remain forever; they will wear out like old clothing. You will change them like a garment and discard them."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 26,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "They will perish, but you remain forever; they will wear out like old clothing. You will change them like a garment and discard them."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 26,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 27,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "But you are always the same; you will live forever. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 27,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "But you are always the same; you will live forever."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 27,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 28,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "The children of your people will live in security. Their children’s children will thrive in your presence.” "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 28,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "The children of your people will live in security. Their children’s children will thrive in your presence.”"
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
